"{\"uid\": \"comicbook.com-anime-news-one-piece-paris-olympics-luffy\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByNick Valdez  One Piecehas made a surprising appearance at the Paris Olympics 2024 thanks to some fun shout outs to Monkey D. Luffy from some pro athletes.One Pieceis currently at its biggest yet as the anime is now in celebration of its 25th anniversary milestone.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0083782299620049e-30, \"text\": \"Luffy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means that the franchise has been showing up in the wildest of places through the year thus far, and it's clear thatEiichiro Oda's original manga and anime franchise is also one step closerto taking over the world as it continues to work through its Final Saga towards its grand finale overall.\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One Piececontinues todominate the world with the newest episodes and manga chapters,and it's clear that Luffy's been influence all sorts of fans all over the world.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0083782299620049e-30, \"text\": \"Luffy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes some of the athletes who have been competing such as Payton Otterdahl, who was representing the United States of America in the shot put and ultimately placed fourth in the world.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Payton\", \"score\": 0.9782155372198749, \"rank\": 0.02226898267300181, \"text\": \"Payton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Payton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Payton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But before doing so, Otterdahl pumped himself with Haki to be like Luffy's Gear Fourth Boundman form.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_Piece\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.106664292872958e-37, \"text\": \"Haki\", \"types\": [\"Q8274\", \"Q386724\", \"Q245068\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_Piece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_Piece\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0083782299620049e-30, \"text\": \"Luffy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monkey_D._Luffy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Check it out:  At the Paris Olympics, the American athlete Payton Otterdahl does Gear 4 pose !One piece influence is CRAZYpic.twitter.com/BtgGRyXzOd  If you wanted to go back and check out theOne Pieceanime from thevery beginning (along with various OVAs, movies, and other specials), you can find the entire back catalog streaming with Crunchyroll with both Japanese and English language dubbed audio.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8689595096094859, \"rank\": 0.1507328384121616, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Payton\", \"score\": 0.9782155372198749, \"rank\": 0.02226898267300181, \"text\": \"Payton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Payton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Payton\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crunchyroll\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crunchyroll\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crunchyroll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crunchyroll\"}, {\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.7262981837603887, \"rank\": 0.3768365173680518, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The newest episodes of the anime,One Piece: Egghead Arc, are now airing weekly and are available to stream with Crunchyroll and Netflix alongside their initial release in Japan.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmer_Fudd\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 5.882091117999622e-13, \"text\": \"Egghead\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmer_Fudd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmer_Fudd\"}, {\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crunchyroll\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crunchyroll\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crunchyroll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crunchyroll\"}, {\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.999999997888608, \"rank\": 2.1103911080544666e-09, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9726081306338777, \"rank\": 0.027082187969622157, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the manga is more your speed, you can also find the newest chapters of theOne Piecemanga (with the three most recent chapters being available for free) with Viz Media's digital Shonen Jump library or Shueisha'sMangaPlus service if you wanted to read ahead to see what's coming next instead.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viz_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Viz Media\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viz_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viz_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonen_Jump_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.5483383678368174, \"rank\": 0.8236914600550831, \"text\": \"Shonen Jump\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonen_Jump_(magazine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonen_Jump_(magazine)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also the entire back catalog of the decades long series available as well.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are still even more ways to enjoyOne Pieceoutside of the anime and manga releases too such as the live-actionOne Pieceseries with Netflix, which is now in the works on Season 2 for a release in the near future.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2126, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.999999997888608, \"rank\": 2.1103911080544666e-09, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also a brand new anime remaking the One Pieceseries from the very beginning with Netflix,The One Piece.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.999999997888608, \"rank\": 2.1103911080544666e-09, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get access to exclusive stories on new releases, movies, shows, comics, anime, games and more!\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up, you confirm that you have read and agree to theTerms of Useand acknowledge ourPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": []}]}"